 of $4\\;$T, for example,\ncorresponds to half a revolution of nuclear spins between two laser pulses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 12:12:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2018 12:39:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-04"}
