ost savings when considering a larger number of\nfuture scenarios during strategic time window assignment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 15:29:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2018 21:43:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-11"}
